What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Organic Cocoa Beverages Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Organic Cocoa Beverages Market

Organic cocoa beverages market is expected to reach USD 3.90 billion by 2028 and grow at a rate of 8.65% in the forecast period 2021 to 2028. Rise in the awareness among consumers of the health benefits of chocolate consumption acts as the vital factor escalating the demand for organic cocoa beverages market in the forecast period of 2021- 2028.

Organic chocolate is chocolate which has been certified organic and is a socially-desirable product for some consumers. It is one of the most extensive used raw materials in the food and beverage industry.

Rise in the awareness among consumers of the health benefits of chocolate consumption is the major driver escalating the market growth, also increase in the application of cocoa in other end-user sectors, such as the cosmetic industry and pharmaceutical industry, rise in the demand from emerging economies and increase in the research and development activities in the market are also the factors driving the organic cocoa beverages market growth. Moreover, rise in the technological advancements and modernization in the production techniques will further create new opportunities for the organic cocoa beverages market manufacturers in the forecast period of 2021- 2028.

However, rise in the cost of research and development activities acts as the major factor acting as a restraint, and will further challenge the growth of organic cocoa beverages market in the forecast period.

